{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"b1bada4b-5176-405e-a47c-bdc63c0d76d7":{"type":"image-banner","blocks":{"template--18525042377005__b1bada4b-5176-405e-a47c-bdc63c0d76d7-168029558339b98ef9-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"About Us","heading_size":"h1"}},"template--18525042377005__b1bada4b-5176-405e-a47c-bdc63c0d76d7-168029558339b98ef9-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"Welcome to Payton James!","text_style":"subtitle"}}},"block_order":["template--18525042377005__b1bada4b-5176-405e-a47c-bdc63c0d76d7-168029558339b98ef9-0","template--18525042377005__b1bada4b-5176-405e-a47c-bdc63c0d76d7-168029558339b98ef9-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/banner-img.png","image_overlay_opacity":0,"image_height":"medium","desktop_content_position":"middle-center","show_text_box":true,"desktop_content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"accent-2","image_behavior":"none","mobile_content_alignment":"center","stack_images_on_mobile":true,"show_text_below":true}},"7b669d59-14a8-4870-a963-d12e2bb23042":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--18525042377005__7b669d59-14a8-4870-a963-d12e2bb23042-16802958151928ded8-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>We are a women-owned e-commerce company specializing in beautifully handcrafted tabletop collections made with raffia palm. Our products are unique and are crafted by skilled women artisans who are dedicated to creating beautiful and sustainable products.<\/p>","text_style":"subtitle"}}},"block_order":["template--18525042377005__7b669d59-14a8-4870-a963-d12e2bb23042-16802958151928ded8-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/product-img-2.png","height":"small","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","image_behavior":"none","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"6b9c5aa2-dd9c-4f69-a29e-62b53d7ada78":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--18525042377005__6b9c5aa2-dd9c-4f69-a29e-62b53d7ada78-16802958151928ded8-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Our founder, Payton James, has always had a passion for fashion design and a degree in fine art from O'More College of Design. Payton started her entrepreneurial journey in 2018 with the launch of her handbag collection. However, it was during the peak of the pandemic in 2020 that she realized her passion for designing home lines, and that's when Payton James Home was born. Payton's vision for the company is to create a line of products that are not only beautiful but also sustainable.<\/p>","text_style":"subtitle"}}},"block_order":["template--18525042377005__6b9c5aa2-dd9c-4f69-a29e-62b53d7ada78-16802958151928ded8-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/about-img.png","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","image_behavior":"none","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"b2d6bbe8-a968-4d15-821c-8fbd318aef5b":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--18525042377005__b2d6bbe8-a968-4d15-821c-8fbd318aef5b-16802958151928ded8-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>At Payton James, we are committed to supporting our local community and women artisans. Our handmade tabletop collection is a testament to the skill and talent of our artisans who pour their heart and soul into each piece. We believe that by supporting women artisans and the local community, we can create a positive impact on the world.<\/p><p><strong>Thank you for choosing Payton James. We hope our passion for design, sustainability, and community shines through in every product we offer.<\/strong><\/p>","text_style":"subtitle"}}},"block_order":["template--18525042377005__b2d6bbe8-a968-4d15-821c-8fbd318aef5